            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-3xl text-white relative font-bold mb-2">Excellent standard and efficient</h3>

            <p class="relative">Right from the beginning James was professional, communicated effectively.
              Work was done to an excellent standard and efficient. Would throughly recommend them.
            </p>
          </div>
        
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="px-6 py-12 md:py-16 md:pl-10 md:pr-0 lg:pl-16">
     
        <blockquote class="mt-6 md:flex md:flex-grow md:flex-col">
          <div class="relative text-lg font-medium text-white md:flex-grow">
            <svg class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-8 w-8 -translate-x-3 -translate-y-2 transform text-gray-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
              <path d="M9.352 4C4.456 7.456 1 13.12 1 19.36c0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.36 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.208-5.472-5.088-5.472-.576 0-1.344.096-1.536.192.48-3.264 3.552-7.104 6.624-9.024L9.352 4zm16.512 0c-4.8 3.456-8.256 9.12-8.256 15.36 0 5.088 3.072 8.064 6.624 8.064 3.264 0 5.856-2.688 5.856-5.856 0-3.168-2.304-5.472-5.184-5.472-.576 0-1.248.096-1.44.192.48-3.264 3.456-7.104 6.528-9.024L25.864 4z" />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-3xl text-white relative font-bold mb-2">Excellent service</h3>
            <p class="relative">Excellent service. They installed our patio and retaining walls. I would definitely recommend these guys to anyone.
            </p>
          </div>
         
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <div class="px-6 py-12 md:py-16 md:pl-10 md:pr-0 lg:pl-16">
     
        <blockquote class="mt-6 md:flex md:flex-grow md:flex-col">
          <div class="relative text-lg font-medium text-white md:flex-grow">
            <svg class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-8 w-8 -translate-x-3 -translate-y-2 transform text-gray-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
